posts.title: NATIONAL VOTER REGISTRATION DAY!  - Check your voter registration status. Many Pedes have discovered that they are inactive!
posts.content:
Confirm your family and friends voter registration status here: https://www.usa.gov/state-election-office

Folks, don't assume you're registered, check, and continue to check until your vote is recorded.

/u/45isthebomb checked their status this morning and reported this:

"How bout that. I checked my status and it was inactive! Thanks for the link."

We must be Too Big To Rig in November and that starts with registering to vote.
